      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a campaign for a conservative candidate in the upcoming midterms. we need a really powerful, stirring speech for a rally. the theme is defending traditional family values against the recent wave of progressive radicalism that's being pushed on our kids. can you draft something unapologetic and strong that really hits those points? thanks.",
