    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit generic. We need to be more specific about what we're actually fighting against. Can you add a section that specifically calls out how these radical reforms in schools are undermining parental rights and trying to replace traditional moral guidance with their own agenda? Use language that makes it clear these aren't just \"differences of opinion\" but an actual threat to our way of life.",
